arts.ttl: Celta Vigo vs Atletico Madrid – Match preview and team news
arts.sum: Celta Vigo entertain Atletico Madrid in a crucial LaLiga encounter on Sunday at Estadio Abanca-Balaídos. The hosts have not beaten Atleti in their last 13 meetings, their longest winless run against the Rojiblancos.
